# Audio Assets Directory

This directory contains audio files for the game:

- `sfx/` - Sound effects (shooting, explosions, etc.)
- `music/` - Background music tracks
- `ui/` - UI sound effects (clicks, notifications, etc.)

## Supported Formats
- MP3 (best compatibility)
- OGG (good compression, open source)
- WAV (uncompressed, larger files)

## Naming Convention
- Use descriptive names: `laser_shoot.mp3`, `enemy_explosion.mp3`
- Keep filenames short and without spaces
- Use consistent naming patterns